# 📌 About

**SPiDER VPN** is a ready-to-deploy VPN Panel based on **VPN-UI / X-UI**.

This project is optimized for:

- ☁️ Railway Cloud
- 🐳 Docker Deployment
- ⚡ Automatic Xray Setup
- 🔥 Simple Installation


---

# ✨ Features

| Feature | Status |
|---|---|
| 🚀 Railway Deploy | ✅ |
| 🐳 Docker Support | ✅ |
| ⚡ Xray Core | ✅ |
| 🔐 VLESS Support | ✅ |
| 🔐 VMess Support | ✅ |
| 🔐 Trojan Support | ✅ |
| 💾 SQLite Database | ✅ |
| 🔄 Auto Start | ✅ |
| 🌐 Cloud Ready | ✅ |


---

# 🚀 Installation Guide


## 1️⃣ Create GitHub Account

First create a GitHub account:

```
https://github.com
```

After creating your account, login.


---

## 2️⃣ Fork This Repository

Open this repository:

```
YOUR_GITHUB_REPOSITORY_LINK
```

Click:

```
Fork
```

Now the project will be copied into your GitHub account.


---

## 3️⃣ Create Railway Account

Go to:

```
https://railway.app
```

Login with GitHub.


---

## 4️⃣ Deploy on Railway

Inside Railway:

```
New Project
        ↓
Deploy from GitHub Repo
        ↓
Select your Fork
        ↓
Deploy
```


Wait until the build finishes.


---

# ⚙️ Railway Configuration


Go to:

```
Project
 ↓
Variables
```

Add:

```
PORT=2083
```


Panel Port:

```
2083
```


---

# 🌐 Open Panel


After deployment:

Go to:

```
Settings
        ↓
Networking
        ↓
Generate Domain
```


Your panel address:

```
https://YOUR-PROJECT.up.railway.app
```


---

# 📜 Logs Check

Successful startup:

```
Starting x-ui

Web server running HTTP on 0.0.0.0:2083

vpn-ui panel listening on port 2083
```


